	<div>Vancouver: 1770 West 7th Ave. Suite 305 Vancouver BC V6J 4Y6 PH 604.681.3030 FX 604.681.2025</div>
	<div>Ottawa: 100 Sparks Street 8th Floor Ottawa ON K1P 5B7 PH 613.916.6215 FX 613.238.9997</div>
	</div>
